| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3747 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b5fc44d3-99c7-53ee-8957-5a2917cc697e"
